Enter into the tomcat9 folder

To execute the servlet start the tomcat server
./startup.sh which is in bin directory

write servlet program into ROOT/webapps/WEB-INF/classes/servlet_pgm

compile it but it will shows error

then set class path of servlet-api.jar file using
javac -cp "path of servlet-api.jar" filename.java

copy the file name into web.xml

and then run that pgm on web server as
localhost:8080/filename

./shutdown.sh to shut down the tomcat server

if web browser gives some error then check it properly
make sure your class is public 
your import statement ,methods are correct
